  m_text: '


    VOLTMETER MANUAL

    

    Purpose:

    Measures voltage difference
    between two nodes.

    

    Connections:

    Red Terminal  -> Positive
    Node

    Black Terminal -> Negative Node

    

    Formula:

    Voltage
    = V(+) - V(-)

    

    Example:

    V(+) = 12V

    V(-) = 0V

    

    Displayed
    Reading:

    12.00 V'
